%e A196840 Sigma n^4 = sum(j^4,j=1..n) =
%e A196840 -(1/30)*n + (1/3)*n^3 +  (1/2)*n^4 + (1/5)*n^5.
%e A196840 For n>=1 this is the sequence A000538(n).
